g.text: Compare fractions by finding a common denominator or using cross products.

div.p: Example: Compare 5/8 and 3/5 using cross products
Example: Compare 7/12 and 5/9 using cross products

ul.li: Use LCD or cross products to compare fractions.
Same numerator: Smaller denominator larger fraction.
Cross products: Multiply diagonally and compare results.
